dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v1.swcomponenttemplate.datatype.units

Interface IUnit

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity, IIdentifiable

    public interface IUnit
extends IEntity, IIdentifiable
    IUnit: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    This is a physical measurement unit. All units that might be defined should stem from SI units. In order to convert one unit into another factor and offset are defined. For the calculation from SI-unit to the defined unit the factor (factorSiToUnit ) and the offset (offsetSiToUnit ) are applied: unit = siUnit * factorSiToUnit + offsetSiToUnit For the calculation from a unit to SI-unit the reciprocal of the factor (factorSiToUnit ) and the negation of the offset (offsetSiToUnit ) are applied: siUnit = (unit - offsetSiToUnit) / factorSiToUnit
